INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (11,1,'Double Duvet Cover Set','\r\nThe Karaca Home Amar Blue 100% Cotton Double Duvet Cover Set offers both style and comfort for your bedroom. Made from high-quality 100% cotton, this duvet cover set ensures a soft and luxurious feel against your skin. The set includes a double-sized duvet cover and matching pillowcases, creating a cohesive look for your bed ensemble.\r\n\r\nWith its elegant blue color and timeless design, the Amar duvet cover set adds a touch of sophistication to any bedroom decor. Whether you prefer a modern or classic style, this set complements a variety of interior themes.\r\n\r\nNot only does the cotton fabric provide breathability and comfort, but it\'s also easy to care for, making maintenance a breeze. Simply machine wash the duvet cover set in cold water and tumble dry on low for best results.\r\n\r\nTransform your bedroom into a cozy retreat with the Karaca Home Amar Blue 100% Cotton Double Duvet Cover Set, offering both beauty and functionality for a restful night\'s sleep.','image_1714476386072.webp','#0033ff','#000000','2000','Istanbul'),(12,1,'Madame Coco Molsheim Lampshade','The Madame Coco Molsheim Lampshade is a stylish and elegant addition to any home decor. Crafted with care and attention to detail, this lampshade boasts a sophisticated design that enhances the ambiance of any room.\r\n\r\nFeaturing high-quality materials and exquisite craftsmanship, the Molsheim Lampshade adds a touch of luxury to your living space. Its timeless design makes it suitable for a variety of interior styles, from traditional to contemporary.\r\n\r\nWith its soft and diffused lighting, this lampshade creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for relaxing evenings or cozy gatherings with friends and family. Whether used as a statement piece in the living room or as a subtle accent in the bedroom, the Madame Coco Molsheim Lampshade adds both style and functionality to your home lighting setup.\r\n\r\nExperience the beauty and elegance of the Madame Coco Molsheim Lampshade and elevate the look of your living space with its refined design and soft illumination.','image_1714476809813.webp','#000000','#ffffff','4500','Istanbul'),(13,2,'Smart Fryer','The Yasomi Y22 White Airfryer is a versatile kitchen appliance designed to make cooking healthier and more convenient. With its sleek white design, this airfryer adds a modern touch to any kitchen countertop.\r\n\r\nPowered by a 1500W motor, the Yasomi Y22 Airfryer quickly and evenly circulates hot air around your food, creating a crispy outer layer while keeping the inside tender and moist. This innovative cooking method allows you to enjoy your favorite fried foods with up to 85% less fat compared to traditional frying methods, making it a healthier alternative for you and your family.\r\n\r\nEquipped with a generous 5-liter capacity, the Smart Fryer provides ample space to cook a variety of dishes, from crispy fries and chicken wings to roasted vegetables and even desserts. Its user-friendly interface and digital controls make it easy to adjust temperature and cooking time according to your preferences, while the built-in smart presets simplify the cooking process for popular dishes.\r\n\r\nCleaning up is a breeze with the Yasomi Y22 Airfryer, thanks to its non-stick cooking basket and removable parts that are dishwasher safe. Whether you\'re cooking for yourself or entertaining guests, this airfryer is sure to become a favorite kitchen companion, helping you prepare delicious and healthier meals with ease.','image_1714476922427.webp','#404040','#000000','1500','Ankara'),(14,2,'Fika Aluminum Cast Pan','The Fika Aluminum Cast Pan is a versatile and durable cookware essential for any kitchen. Crafted from high-quality aluminum, this cast pan offers excellent heat conductivity and distribution, ensuring even cooking results every time.\r\n\r\nWith its sturdy construction and non-stick surface, the Fika Aluminum Cast Pan is ideal for a wide range of cooking tasks, from frying and saut√©ing to searing and braising. Its deep sides and wide cooking surface provide ample space for cooking large quantities of food, making it perfect for preparing family meals or entertaining guests.\r\n\r\nThe pan\'s aluminum construction makes it lightweight and easy to handle, while its heat-resistant handle ensures a comfortable and secure grip during use. Whether you\'re cooking breakfast, lunch, or dinner, the Fika Aluminum Cast Pan is up to the task, delivering delicious and flavorful dishes with ease.\r\n\r\nEasy to clean and maintain, this cast pan is dishwasher safe for convenient cleanup after cooking. Add the Fika Aluminum Cast Pan to your kitchen arsenal and enjoy versatile cooking performance and exceptional durability for years to come.','image_1714477027468.webp','#4d4d4d','#4995bc','5000','Bursa'),(15,3,'Crocs Crocband Unisex Slippers','The Crocs Crocband Unisex Slippers combine comfort and style for everyday wear. Featuring the iconic Crocband design, these slippers offer a classic look that\'s both casual and versatile.\r\n\r\nConstructed from Crocs\' signature Croslite material, these slippers provide lightweight cushioning and support, ensuring all-day comfort for your feet. The contoured footbed conforms to the shape of your foot, while the heel strap provides a secure fit and added stability.\r\n\r\nWith their slip-on design and easy-to-clean construction, these Crocband slippers are perfect for wearing around the house, running errands, or relaxing outdoors. The ventilated upper ensures breathability, while the non-marking outsole offers traction and durability on a variety of surfaces.\r\n\r\nAvailable in a range of colors and sizes, the Crocs Crocband Unisex Slippers are a must-have addition to your footwear collection. Whether you\'re lounging at home or stepping out for a casual outing, these slippers provide comfort and style wherever you go.','image_1714477095812.jpg','#000000','#00aaff','1000','Ankara'),(16,3,'Calvin Klein Zippered Bag','The Calvin Klein Zippered Adjustable Shoulder Strap Bag (Women\'s Bag K60K610275 Bds) is a stylish and practical accessory for modern women. Crafted from high-quality materials, this bag offers both durability and sophistication, making it suitable for various occasions.\r\n\r\nFeaturing a zippered closure, this shoulder bag provides secure storage for your belongings while on the go. The adjustable shoulder strap allows you to customize the fit for comfortable wear, whether you prefer to carry it over the shoulder or across the body.\r\n\r\nWith its sleek design and minimalist aesthetic, the Calvin Klein shoulder bag complements a wide range of outfits, from casual ensembles to more formal attire. The iconic Calvin Klein logo adds a touch of luxury to the bag, making it a fashionable choice for everyday use.\r\n\r\nDesigned with practicality in mind, this bag features multiple interior compartments and pockets, allowing you to organize your essentials efficiently. Whether you\'re heading to work, running errands, or meeting friends for brunch, the Calvin Klein Zippered Adjustable Shoulder Strap Bag is the perfect accessory to carry your essentials in style.','image_1714477200997.jpg','','','1055','Izmir'),(17,4,'Compact Wireless Mouse','The Compact Wireless Mouse is a small and portable input device designed for use with computers and laptops. It utilizes wireless technology, typically Bluetooth or a USB receiver, to connect to the device it controls without the need for cables. This mouse is characterized by its small size and lightweight design, making it convenient for travel and use in confined spaces. Despite its compact form factor, it provides the functionality of a traditional mouse, including left and right-click buttons, a scroll wheel, and often additional programmable buttons for customizable functionality. The Compact Wireless Mouse offers users the freedom to control their devices wirelessly, enhancing convenience and reducing clutter on their desks or workspaces.','image_1714487578339.webp','#1c1c1c','#fafafa','1024','Bursa'),(18,4,'HD Smart LED TV','The Samsung 50CU8000 is a 50-inch smart LED TV featuring Crystal 4K Ultra HD resolution, providing stunning clarity and lifelike visuals for an immersive viewing experience. This television is equipped with a built-in satellite receiver, allowing users to access a wide range of satellite channels without the need for an external receiver. With its smart functionality, the Samsung 50CU8000 enables users to stream content from popular online platforms, such as Netflix, YouTube, and more, directly on the TV screen. It also offers various connectivity options, including HDMI and USB ports, for connecting external devices like gaming consoles, Blu-ray players, and USB storage devices. Additionally, the TV comes with advanced features such as HDR (High Dynamic Range) support, providing enhanced contrast and color accuracy, and smart voice assistant compatibility for hands-free control. With its sleek design and cutting-edge technology, the Samsung 50CU8000 delivers an exceptional entertainment experience for users at home.','image_1714487677140.webp','#a6a6a6','#140000','10000','Izmir'),(19,5,'Samsung EB-P5300X Power Bank','\r\nThe Samsung EB-P5300X is a high-capacity power bank with a capacity of 20,000 mAh, allowing users to charge their devices multiple times while on the go. It features 25W Super Fast Charging technology, supporting both Quick Charge (QC) and Power Delivery (PD) protocols, ensuring rapid charging for compatible devices. This power bank is equipped with multiple ports, including USB Type-C and USB Type-A, enabling users to charge multiple devices simultaneously. The USB Type-C port supports both input and output, allowing for fast recharging of the power bank itself as well as charging of compatible devices. With its compact and portable design, the Samsung EB-P5300X is an ideal companion for travel, outdoor activities, or everyday use, providing reliable power whenever and wherever it\'s needed.\r\n\r\n\r\n','image_1714487850425.jpeg','#ff0000','#ff70d2','10000','Kayseri'),(20,5,'Simple Living Picnic and Camping Chair','The Simple Living Picnic and Camping Chair is a lightweight and portable seating solution designed for outdoor activities such as picnics, camping, hiking, and other recreational events. It features a sturdy yet lightweight frame made of durable materials such as aluminum or steel, providing stability and support while remaining easy to transport. The chair typically includes a foldable design, allowing it to be compactly stored and carried in a carrying bag or backpack when not in use. The fabric seat and backrest are designed for comfort, providing a comfortable place to sit and relax during outdoor adventures. With its simple and practical design, the Simple Living Picnic and Camping Chair offers a convenient and comfortable seating option for outdoor enthusiasts of all ages.','image_1714487974854.jpeg','#ff0000','#121212','10000','Samsun');
